Virtual Host Configuration

- Please set the document route of your virtual host to the www folder
- Create a subdomain (e.g. resource.yourdomain.com) and put your css/images and javascript here

Secure Database Setup (Optional)

- Modify the credentials/apache.conf file to contain your database credentials
- Configure your apache virtual host configuration to include the credentials/apache.conf file

Adding Zend Classes (Optional)

- Download the Zend framework
- Copy the classes you want into package/Zend
